description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 2 of 3 of the live October match up between The Dragons and The Ninjas.
The sport is real. The wrestling is un-scripted, the girls are determined and strong. Like in any sport, top athletes are at risk. These girls put it all out on the line, 100%. When injuries happen we are all affected in one way or another. The sport is real. The wrestling is...
title: Injuries are part of the sport, & the sport is brutal,
